---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
---
<Layout title="Backstage Access">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 w-full mt-8">
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase text-center">Backstage Access</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-bold mb-12 text-center">Wedding Party Eyes Only</p>
    
    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-amber-600 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">The Pre-Party (Bachelor Weekend)</h2>
      <p class="text-amber-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Dates TBD • Cabin in the Woods</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>We're doing a combined camping trip in the middle of nowhere. Expect cheap beer, a fire pit, and extremely loud music. We are handling the Airbnb booking, so just be ready to venmo when we text the group thread.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-orange-700 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Rehearsal & Dinner</h2>
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Call Time: 6:00 PM • TUI Demo Stairs</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Rehearsal kicks off at 6:00 PM. After that, we are dragging the entire wedding party to the Trapped Under Ice Demo stairs to get photos, because that's sick as hell. Dinner to follow immediately after.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-zinc-100 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Day-Of Logistics & Photos</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Call Time: TBD</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>We are still sorting out exactly where the wedding party is staying, but expect to be getting ready together. We will update this page with exact call times for hair, makeup, and pre-show photos as we get closer to the date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-emerald-600 shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-zinc-100 font-display mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Day-Of Load-In</h2>
      <p class="text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-4">Call Time: 1:00 PM Sharp</p>
      <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Do not be late. Show up to the venue completely ready. We are doing wedding party photos first so we can hit the bar before the ceremony starts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>